on his part?

14:25.800 --> 14:30.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
RHODES: Well, look, we
believe that there is
one president at a time.

14:32.867 --> 14:34.700 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Frankly, after January
20, the president-elect
