on these issues.

14:36.800 --> 14:41.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Again, I would say, it's very
important, this is bipartisan
position to oppose continued

14:43.433 --> 14:47.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
