saying he's going to undo this
as soon as he takes office

16:31.833 --> 16:32.633 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in a few weeks?

16:32.633 --> 16:37.633 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Is it worth it?

16:40.300 --> 16:45.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOODRUFF: Ben Rhodes, deputy
national security advisor to
the president -- thank you very

17:06.100 --> 17:09.000 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
much.

17:09.000 --> 17:14.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
RHODES: Thank you.

