17:33.367 --> 17:37.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
YANG: Are the president- elect's
tweets and comments signaling
a change in U.S. nuclear

17:37.300 --> 17:38.800 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
weapons policy?

17:38.800 --> 17:41.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
