17:41.300 --> 17:45.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For that, we turn to Matthew
Kroenig, an associate
professor at Georgetown
University who's written

17:48.300 --> 17:51.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
