called for under an
existing treaty with Russia?

20:04.200 --> 20:09.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KROENIG: Well, the existing
treaty with Russia, the new
START treaty was signed in 2011.

20:09.100 --> 20:14.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
