if this is a continuation of
the Obama policy to modernize

22:32.400 --> 22:35.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the arsenal, you think that even
the Obama policy is a bad idea?

22:35.833 --> 22:37.467 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Is that what I take
from what you said?

22:37.467 --> 22:39.467 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CIRINCIONE: Absolutely.

22:39.467 --> 22:42.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The very first thing General
Mattis is going to find out
when he takes over as secretary

22:42.133 --> 22:45.967 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of defense is we don't have
the money to pay for the
programs that are on the books.

22:45.967 --> 22:50.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
